
How to cite Hyrax

Use the following text within your publications to cite Hyrax

For data use: "Data were accessed using the Hyrax data server, version
<ver>, running at <locaction>."

For providing data: "Data were made avalable using the HYrax data
server, version <ver>."

To find the DOI for the current version of Hyrax (or recent previous
versions), look on the GitHUb pages for the OLFS and note the DOI for
that software. This is the DO for the whole server and includes the
DOI for the backend server and DAP library distributions.

The OLFS GitHub page is https://github.com/OPENDAP/olfs.

